/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>1. The Best Beaches of Koh Lipe<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Koh Lipe has some truly stunning beaches to relax on. There are three main beaches and a few smaller less-visited ones. The beaches are wide, so you don&#x2019;t have to worry about a lack of space.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sunrise Beach<\/strong> (west) is obviously best for sunrises and has the best beach bars. Visit the small secret beach opposite Ten Moons Lipe Resort.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123131\/best-things-to-do-koh-lipe-beaches-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do koh lipe beaches\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do koh lipe beaches\" data-id=\"19752\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123131\/best-things-to-do-koh-lipe-beaches.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=19752\" class=\"wp-image-19752 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123131\/best-things-to-do-koh-lipe-beaches-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123131\/best-things-to-do-koh-lipe-beaches-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123131\/best-things-to-do-koh-lipe-beaches-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123131\/best-things-to-do-koh-lipe-beaches-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123131\/best-things-to-do-koh-lipe-beaches-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.