he island for the picturesque Pitiusas Beach.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/koh-lipe-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find all hotels on the island<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123121\/koh-lipe-thailand-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"koh lipe thailand\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"koh lipe thailand\" data-id=\"19759\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123121\/koh-lipe-thailand.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=19759\" class=\"wp-image-19759 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123121\/koh-lipe-thailand-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123121\/koh-lipe-thailand-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123121\/koh-lipe-thailand-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123121\/koh-lipe-thailand-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123121\/koh-lipe-thailand-226x338.jpg 2