erest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123032\/thigns-to-do-koh-lipe-kayaking-1080x778.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Kayaking is most popular at Sunrise Beach, especially at the northern tip where you can kayak to a tiny island named <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/3sfLuqE8RDuGoST39\">Ko Kra<\/a>. The price for renting a kayak on Koh Lipe ranges from 150 &#x2013; 250 baht per hour.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read about:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/thailand\/khao-sok-national-park-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Khao Sok National Park in Thailand (opens in a new tab)\">Khao Sok National Park in Thailand<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>3. Koh Adang Day Trip<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Koh Adang is Koh Lipe&#x2019;s much bigger neighboring brother. It is easy to reach by longtail boat transfer, which can be found at Sunrise Beach. <\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19745&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23123016\/best-things-to-do-koh-lipe-thailand.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank