thailand\/krabi\/\" target=\"_blank\">Krabi<\/a>, either take a minivan (5 hours) to <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Pak Bara Pier (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/pak-bara\/koh-lipe\" target=\"_blank\">Pak Bara Pier<\/a> and a ferry (2 hours) to Koh Lipe. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/pak-bara\/koh-lipe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Get your tickets here (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get tickets from Pak Bara here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Alternatively, take the ferry (7 hours) from Krabi Town (Klong Jilad Pier) to Koh Lipe. The waters are known to be rough so if you&#x2019;re uncomfortable with that, the first option would be best.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/klong-jilad-pier\/koh-lipe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get tickets from Krabi here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Bangkok to Koh Lipe<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>From Bangkok, fly to Hat Yai Airport and take the ferry from Pak Bara pier.<strong> <\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-to-koh-lipe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find the cheapest flight tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23122931\/guide-thailand-saltinourhair-531x810.jpg\" alt=\"guide thailand saltinourhair\"><\/noscript><img width=\"222\" height=\"338\" alt=\"guide thailand saltinourhair\" data-id=\"19849\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23122931\/guide-thailand-saltinourhair.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=19849\" class=\"wp-image-19849 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 531px) 100vw, 531px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23122931\/guide-thailand-saltinourhair-531x810.jpg 531w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\